62 Serie A}}\n\n==== League table ====\n{{:1961-62 Serie A|showteam=MIL}}\n\n====Matches====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 27 August 1961\n|time = \n|round = 1\n|team1 = [[Vicenza Calcio|Lanerossi]]\n|team2 = Milan\n|score = 0-3\n|report = \n|location = [[Vicenza]] \n|stadium = [[Stadio Romeo Menti]]\n|attendance = {{formatnum:20000}}\n|referee = Gennaro Marchese\n|goals1 = \n|goals2 = {{Goal|29||39}}[[Jose Altafini|Altafini]]<br />{{Goal|55|pen}} [[Jimmy Greaves|Greaves]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 3 September 1961\n|time  = \n|round = 2\n|team1 = Milan\n|team2 = Catania\n|score  = 3-0\n|report = \n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio San Siro|San Siro]]\n|attendance = {{formatnum:26900}}\n|referee = Samani\n|goals1 = Barison {{Goal|50}}<br />Radice {{Goal|68}}<br />[[Cesare Maldini|Maldini]] {{Goal|72}}\n|goals2 = \n|result = W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 10 September 1961\n|time  = \n|round = 3\n|team1 = [[Palermo]]\n|team2 = Milan\n|score  = 0-0\n|report = \n|location = [[Palermo]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio La Favorita]]\n|attendance = {{formatnum:37500}}\n|referee = Gastone Roversi\n|goals1 = \n|goals2 = \n|result=D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 13 September 1961\n|time  = \n|round = 4\n|team1 = Milan\n|team2 = [[Udinese]]\n|score  = 4-3\n|report = \n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio San Siro|San Siro]]\n|attendance = {{formatnum:22000}}\n|referee = Antonio Sbardella\n|goals1 = [[Jimmy Greaves|Greaves]] {{Goal|10||24|pen}}<br />Sassi {{Goal|22|aut}}<br />Pivatelli {{Goal|49}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|30||82}} Pentrelli<br />{{Goal|36}} Canella\n|result = W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 17 September 1961\n|time = \n|round = 5\n|team1 = [[Bologna F.C.|Bologna]]\n|team2 = Milan\n|score = 1-0\n|report = \n|location = [[Bologna]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Renato Dall'Ara|Comunale]]\n|attendance = {{formatnum:32500}}\n|referee = Bruno De Marchi\n|goals1 = Bulgarelli {{Goal|55}}\n|goals2 = \n|result=L\n}}\n