ppe Savoldi|Savoldi]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|date = 30 November 1975\n|time = 14:30 [[UTC+1]]\n|round = 7\n|team1 = [[A.S. Roma|Roma]]\n|team2 = Torino\n|score= 1-1\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1975/12565/\n|location = [[Rome|Roma]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Olimpico|Olimpico]]\n|attendance = 53.079\n|referee= [[Luigi Agnolin|Agnolin]]\n|result=D\n|goals1 = [[Piergiorgio Negrisolo|Negrisolo]] {{Goal|73}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|68}} [[Francesco Graziani|Graziani]]\n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|date = 7 December 1975\n|time = 14:30 [[UTC+1]]\n|round = 8\n|team1 = Torino\n|team2 = [[Juventus]]\n|score= 2-0\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1975/12647/\n|location= [[Torino]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Olimpico Grande Torino|Comunale]]\n|attendance = 52 747\n|referee = [[Alberto Michelotti|Michelotti]]\n|result=W\n|goals1 = [[Francesco Graziani|Graziani]] {{Goal|75}}<br />[[Paolo Pulici|Pulici]] {{Goal|78|pen}}\n|goals2 = \n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|date = 14 December 1975\n|time = 14:30 [[UTC+1]]\n|round = 9\n|team1 = [[A.C. Milan|Milan]]\n|team2 = Torino\n|score= 1-2\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1975/12721/\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio San Siro|San Siro]]\n|attendance = 37 409\n|referee\t = [[Giulio Ciacci|Ciacci]]\n|result=W\n|goals1 = [[Aldo Maldera|Maldera]] {{Goal|51}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|16}} [[Renato Zaccarelli|Zaccarelli]]<br />{{Goal|84}} [[Francesco Graziani|Graziani]]\n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|date = 21 December 1975\n|time = 14:30 [[UTC+1]]\n|round = 10\n|team1 = Torino\n|team2 = [[Como]]\n|score= 1-0\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1975/12583/\n|location = [[Torino]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Olimpico Grande Torino|Comunale]]\n|attendance = 29.924\n|referee = [[Enzo Barbaresco|Barbaresco]]\n|result=W\n|goals1 = [[Francesco Graziani|Graziani]] {{Goal|47}}\n|goals2 = \n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|date = 4 \tJanuary 1976\n|time = 14:30 [[UTC+1]]\n|round = 11\n|team1 = [[